  "instructions": [
    "1. Preheat grill to medium-high heat.",
    "2. Cut salmon and pineapple into 1-inch pieces.",
    "3. Thread salmon and pineapple onto skewers, leaving space between each piece.",
    "4. In a small bowl, whisk together soy sauce, brown sugar, ginger, and garlic.",
    "5. Brush the glaze mixture onto both sides of the salmon and pineapple.",
    "6. Season with salt and pepper to taste.",
    "7. Grill skewers for 8-10 minutes per side, or until salmon is cooked through.",
    "8. Serve immediately and garnish with fresh cilantro, if desired."
